	<h1 class="title">被艺术家们的手指一碰，圣诞树就变成了这样</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/194153/small/194153.jpg?1454682827" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">徐婧艾 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-08 08:30:03 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/18654/medium/18654.jpg?1449542234" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


